item.title: Analysis: Climate Entrepreneurs in the Middle East
item.description: This week, Leah Hickert speaks with Will Todman, deputy director and senior fellow with the CSIS Middle East Program, about how entrepreneurs can help regional governments adapt to climate change. Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/CSIS1853412217
